##1.  Import ova file in VirtualBox
## Choose Linux other OS
##2.  To allow ssh connections with password
## Edit the /etc/ssh/sshd_config file.
## Change PasswordAuthentication and ChallengeResponseAuthentication to yes
##3. run "source /usr/local/greenplum-db-5.0.0/greenplum_path.sh" before running psql
##4. Connect to db
## psql -U gpadmin -h localhost -p 5432 postgres
